<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>This section is empty.</b> <small>You can help by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Dari_(Persian)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=" class="external text" rel="nofollow">adding to it</a>.</small></td>
