<li id="cite_note-Dari-language-9">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Dari-language_9-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Dari-language_9-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <span class="citation web"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/151550/Dari-language" class="external text" rel="nofollow">"Dari language"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Encyclop%C3%A6dia_Britannica" title="Encyclopædia Britannica">Encyclopædia Britannica</a> Online<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/151550/Dari-language" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/151550/Dari-language</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2010-12-07</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Dari+language&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BEncyclop%C3%A6dia+Britannica%5D%5D+Online&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2FEBchecked%2Ftopic%2F151550%2FDari-language&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Dari_(Persian)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
